title: Have A Positive Mindset | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Have A Positive Mindset | Joel Osteen
description:
In order to become everything God created you to be, you need to have the right mindset. When you choose to believe, you're releasing your faith for greater things! 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
